cu.explanation_en: Setting drb_integrity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause security configuration failure and prevent proper DRB integrity setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause RF simulation configuration failure and disrupt radio frequency operations.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型名稱設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致 RF 模擬配置失敗，並干擾無線電頻率操作。
